00:00:17.750 --> 00:00:20.553 position:10% line:89% align:start
- [Ruka] Go ahead, they said.

00:00:20.586 --> 00:00:22.255 position:21% line:89% align:start
So I opened my eyes.

00:00:24.824 --> 00:00:28.060 position:19% line:89% align:start
I was inside the ocean.

00:00:29.428 --> 00:00:32.231 position:27% line:89% align:start
(wondrous music)

00:00:34.834 --> 00:00:37.236 position:33% line:83% align:start
My mom and I
reached out our hands.

00:00:42.575 --> 00:00:45.044 position:35% line:89% align:start
(chuckling)

00:00:46.612 --> 00:00:48.681 position:16% line:89% align:start
The fish all followed me,

00:00:51.484 --> 00:00:52.418 position:24% line:89% align:start
everywhere I went.

00:00:53.486 --> 00:00:56.422 position:24% line:89% align:start
(mysterious music)

00:01:03.830 --> 00:01:06.232 position:24% line:83% align:start
These are memories
from when I was little.

00:01:11.170 --> 00:01:14.441 position:19% line:89% align:start
(dramatic violin music)

00:01:22.482 --> 00:01:23.684 position:16% line:89% align:start
- [Man] Is this the song?

00:01:27.287 --> 00:01:28.488 position:44% line:89% align:start
- No.

00:01:28.522 --> 00:01:30.824 position:16% line:83% align:start
These whales are singing
in response to the song.

00:01:33.260 --> 00:01:35.262 position:24% line:89% align:start
(dolphins clicking)

00:01:35.295 --> 00:01:37.631 position:16% line:83% align:start
- [Man] The dolphins are
migrating in response to it.

00:01:38.665 --> 00:01:40.133 position:10% line:89% align:start
It's categorically different

00:01:40.167 --> 00:01:41.335 position:13% line:89% align:start
from any other whale song.

00:01:47.507 --> 00:01:51.578 position:7% line:83% align:start
- [Dehdeh] It's still far, but
it's gradually getting closer.

00:01:52.646 --> 00:01:55.415 position:27% line:89% align:start
(waves crashing)

00:01:58.352 --> 00:02:01.154 position:27% line:89% align:start
(dramatic music)

00:02:07.829 --> 00:02:10.632 position:27% line:89% align:start
(waves crashing)

00:02:19.474 --> 00:02:21.809 position:7% line:89% align:start
From the star, from the stars,

00:02:23.277 --> 00:02:24.545 position:19% line:89% align:start
the sea is the mother.

00:02:31.853 --> 00:02:33.888 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's finally time.

00:02:33.921 --> 00:02:36.658 position:27% line:89% align:start
(dramatic music)

00:02:56.779 --> 00:02:59.648 position:27% line:89% align:start
(seagulls cawing)

00:03:28.343 --> 00:03:30.879 position:30% line:89% align:start
(gate rumbling)

00:03:34.950 --> 00:03:37.820 position:27% line:89% align:start
(heavy breathing)

00:03:55.805 --> 00:03:57.372 position:33% line:89% align:start
- [Ruka] Yes!

00:03:57.406 --> 00:03:58.373 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm flying!

00:03:59.709 --> 00:04:02.344 position:35% line:89% align:start
(cheering)

00:04:02.377 --> 00:04:04.013 position:24% line:89% align:start
- Great shot, Ruka!

00:04:04.047 --> 00:04:05.648 position:5% line:89% align:start
You're light on your feet today!

00:04:09.753 --> 00:04:11.654 position:27% line:89% align:start
(insect chirping)

00:04:11.688 --> 00:04:13.623 position:24% line:83% align:start
- [Ruka] Of course
I'm light on my feet!

00:04:13.656 --> 00:04:15.024 position:13% line:89% align:start
Summer break starts today.

00:04:15.058 --> 00:04:17.292 position:35% line:83% align:start
In summer,
my whole body feels light.

00:04:18.360 --> 00:04:19.462 position:27% line:89% align:start
- [Friend] Nice!

00:04:19.496 --> 00:04:20.530 position:10% line:89% align:start
- [Friend] Ruka, great shot!

00:04:20.563 --> 00:04:23.366 position:35% line:89% align:start
(laughing)

00:04:23.399 --> 00:04:24.768 position:30% line:83% align:start
- Ruka, you're
doing great today!

00:04:24.801 --> 00:04:25.935 position:24% line:89% align:start
- Way to go, Ruka!

00:04:27.804 --> 00:04:30.573 position:10% line:83% align:start
- Oh, she's gotta be careful
when she's doing this well.

00:04:30.607 --> 00:04:31.407 position:41% line:89% align:start
- Huh?

00:04:40.884 --> 00:04:42.352 position:30% line:89% align:start
- Oops, my bad.

00:04:45.889 --> 00:04:47.724 position:30% line:83% align:start
That's what you
get for showing off.

00:04:52.762 --> 00:04:55.632 position:27% line:89% align:start
(whistle blowing)

00:04:57.768 --> 00:04:59.970 position:35% line:89% align:start
(groaning)

00:05:02.106 --> 00:05:03.473 position:13% line:89% align:start
- What happened, your nose?

00:05:03.506 --> 00:05:04.474 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:05:04.507 --> 00:05:06.677 position:19% line:83% align:start
- Ruka's elbow, it hit
her on that last shot.

00:05:07.812 --> 00:05:10.915 position:21% line:83% align:start
- [Girl] I think she
did it on purpose.

00:05:10.948 --> 00:05:13.517 position:30% line:83% align:start
- Well, she may
have a broken nose.

00:05:13.551 --> 00:05:14.919 position:7% line:89% align:start
Take her to the nurse's office.

00:05:17.855 --> 00:05:22.893 position:24% line:89% align:start
(groaning)(sobbing)

00:05:22.927 --> 00:05:25.396 position:27% line:83% align:start
- Ruka, you went
too far this time.

00:05:25.429 --> 00:05:28.065 position:13% line:83% align:start
- Yeah, I know she tripped
you and all, but still.

00:05:29.767 --> 00:05:30.634 position:38% line:89% align:start
- But...

00:05:34.405 --> 00:05:35.606 position:35% line:89% align:start
But she...

00:05:35.639 --> 00:05:37.374 position:30% line:89% align:start
- [Coach] Ruka!

00:05:37.408 --> 00:05:38.042 position:41% line:89% align:start
- She--

00:05:38.075 --> 00:05:39.810 position:41% line:89% align:start
- Ruka!

00:05:39.844 --> 00:05:42.012 position:27% line:83% align:start
I want to see you
in my office, please.

00:05:45.883 --> 00:05:48.452 position:33% line:89% align:start
(fan blowing)

00:05:48.819 --> 00:05:49.921 position:41% line:89% align:start
(sighs)

00:05:49.955 --> 00:05:52.389 position:10% line:83% align:start
So this is how we're starting
our summer break, is it?

00:05:53.824 --> 00:05:56.660 position:10% line:83% align:start
You really enjoy being quite
the troublemaker, don't you?

00:05:56.694 --> 00:05:57.863 position:24% line:89% align:start
Teammate, opponent.

00:05:57.896 --> 00:05:59.396 position:13% line:89% align:start
How many has it been, huh?

00:06:01.465 --> 00:06:03.601 position:24% line:83% align:start
So tell me, why did
you hurt her like that?

00:06:05.203 --> 00:06:06.503 position:44% line:89% align:start
Well?

00:06:06.537 --> 00:06:07.404 position:27% line:89% align:start
Anything to say?

00:06:08.472 --> 00:06:11.676 position:19% line:89% align:start
- Well, she started it.

00:06:11.710 --> 00:06:14.713 position:27% line:83% align:start
- So none of this
is your fault, huh?

00:06:14.746 --> 00:06:16.915 position:24% line:83% align:start
- [Ruka] That's not
what I meant.

00:06:20.852 --> 00:06:23.088 position:10% line:89% align:start
- So, this was all her fault.

00:06:24.589 --> 00:06:25.590 position:30% line:89% align:start
All right then.

00:06:30.562 --> 00:06:33.431 position:5% line:89% align:start
Well, I need to go check on her.

00:06:34.599 --> 00:06:36.668 position:30% line:83% align:start
I might have to
take her to the hospital.

00:06:37.702 --> 00:06:38.737 position:27% line:89% align:start
You can go home.

00:06:40.239 --> 00:06:41.107 position:41% line:89% align:start
- Okay.

00:06:45.844 --> 00:06:48.713 position:30% line:83% align:start
Why didn't you
send me to the nurse too?

00:06:48.747 --> 00:06:50.515 position:27% line:83% align:start
- [Coach] Oh, and
one more thing.

00:06:52.218 --> 00:06:54.786 position:33% line:83% align:start
If you're not
going to apologize,

00:06:54.819 --> 00:06:56.454 position:10% line:89% align:start
no need to come to practice.

00:07:09.902 --> 00:07:12.504 position:33% line:89% align:start
(zipper zips)

00:07:13.505 --> 00:07:16.175 position:27% line:89% align:start
(heavy breathing)

00:07:52.279 --> 00:07:55.015 position:30% line:89% align:start
(train running)

00:07:59.819 --> 00:08:01.620 position:7% line:89% align:start
- Today was just the first day,

00:08:03.857 --> 00:08:07.660 position:19% line:83% align:start
but now my summer break
is already over.

00:08:09.830 --> 00:08:12.899 position:21% line:89% align:start
(somber piano music)

00:08:46.867 --> 00:08:47.734 position:38% line:89% align:start
Aw, man!

00:08:49.803 --> 00:08:51.538 position:21% line:89% align:start
I can't fly anymore.

00:08:59.679 --> 00:09:02.884 position:21% line:89% align:start
(lighthearted music)

00:09:02.917 --> 00:09:05.186 position:33% line:89% align:start
(Ruka sighs)

00:09:19.700 --> 00:09:21.269 position:24% line:83% align:start
- So, what are you
doing on break?

00:09:21.302 --> 00:09:23.071 position:24% line:89% align:start
- Celebrating fun.

00:09:23.104 --> 00:09:25.239 position:30% line:83% align:start
- I'm jealous,
I want to go on a trip!

00:09:25.273 --> 00:09:27.308 position:19% line:83% align:start
- I'll take care of the
team stuff before I go.

00:09:27.341 --> 00:09:28.276 position:33% line:83% align:start
- Sounds like
you're gonna be busy.

00:09:28.309 --> 00:09:29.243 position:27% line:89% align:start
- Yeah, it does!

00:09:29.277 --> 00:09:31.679 position:33% line:83% align:start
I don't think
my family's going anywhere.

00:09:31.712 --> 00:09:33.114 position:24% line:83% align:start
We're just visiting
the family grave.

00:09:33.147 --> 00:09:34.383 position:10% line:89% align:start
- Hey, want to go to a movie?

00:09:34.416 --> 00:09:35.350 position:35% line:89% align:start
- Totally!

00:09:35.384 --> 00:09:36.050 position:30% line:89% align:start
Would love to.

00:09:36.084 --> 00:09:37.352 position:7% line:89% align:start
- [Girl] Yeah, me too, I'm in.

00:09:37.386 --> 00:09:38.686 position:16% line:89% align:start
- [Girl] Cool, let's go!

00:09:40.988 --> 00:09:44.058 position:21% line:89% align:start
(lighthearted music)

00:09:59.674 --> 00:10:02.211 position:5% line:89% align:start
- I wonder how badly I hurt her.

00:10:05.347 --> 00:10:06.882 position:41% line:89% align:start
But...

00:10:06.915 --> 00:10:09.918 position:21% line:89% align:start
(somber piano music)

00:10:19.328 --> 00:10:22.664 position:33% line:89% align:start
(Ruka gasps)

00:10:22.698 --> 00:10:23.832 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's been so long.

00:10:26.802 --> 00:10:27.870 position:33% line:89% align:start
The aquarium.

00:10:34.109 --> 00:10:36.879 position:27% line:89% align:start
(dramatic music)

00:10:48.358 --> 00:10:50.226 position:24% line:83% align:start
- [Woman] Next up,
Enokura Aquarium.

00:10:50.260 --> 00:10:52.195 position:5% line:89% align:start
We will be arriving momentarily.

00:10:57.933 --> 00:10:58.967 position:24% line:89% align:start
- Wonder Aquarium!

00:11:02.038 --> 00:11:03.006 position:16% line:89% align:start
See the Wonder Aquarium!

00:11:03.039 --> 00:11:03.872 position:38% line:89% align:start
Welcome.

00:11:03.907 --> 00:11:05.909 position:35% line:83% align:start
Today's the
first day of the exhibit.

00:11:05.942 --> 00:11:07.043 position:38% line:83% align:start
- Ready?
- Enjoy!

00:11:07.076 --> 00:11:08.478 position:35% line:89% align:start
(chuckling)

00:11:08.511 --> 00:11:09.445 position:38% line:83% align:start
Bye bye!
- Thanks a lot.

00:11:09.479 --> 00:11:10.947 position:38% line:83% align:start
- Thanks.
- Bye bye!

00:11:10.980 --> 00:11:11.814 position:33% line:89% align:start
Can I see it?

00:11:12.515 --> 00:11:13.483 position:30% line:89% align:start
- Here you go.

00:11:13.516 --> 00:11:15.185 position:33% line:89% align:start
- Oh, thanks.

00:11:20.890 --> 00:11:22.325 position:24% line:89% align:start
- Wait, excuse me.

00:11:22.358 --> 00:11:24.127 position:30% line:83% align:start
But aren't you
Mr. Azumi's daughter?

00:11:26.396 --> 00:11:27.297 position:41% line:89% align:start
- Huh?

00:11:27.330 --> 00:11:28.498 position:33% line:89% align:start
Ruka's here?

00:11:28.532 --> 00:11:29.533 position:24% line:89% align:start
You recognized her?

00:11:29.567 --> 00:11:31.502 position:16% line:83% align:start
- (chuckles) She has your
eyes, so it was easy.

00:11:31.535 --> 00:11:32.802 position:7% line:89% align:start
Plus she came here all the time

00:11:32.835 --> 00:11:34.170 position:13% line:89% align:start
when she was a little girl.

00:11:34.204 --> 00:11:35.138 position:24% line:89% align:start
- Why is she here?

00:11:35.171 --> 00:11:37.040 position:13% line:89% align:start
I'm tied up at the moment.

00:11:37.073 --> 00:11:38.409 position:24% line:83% align:start
Can you tell her to
come find me?

00:11:38.442 --> 00:11:40.109 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'm behind the big tank.

00:11:40.143 --> 00:11:41.144 position:33% line:89% align:start
Yeah, thanks.

00:11:42.111 --> 00:11:44.147 position:7% line:89% align:start
- Chief, the sardines are here.

00:11:44.180 --> 00:11:45.215 position:33% line:89% align:start
- Oh, right.

00:11:46.283 --> 00:11:47.917 position:7% line:89% align:start
- I'll show you where they are.

00:11:49.220 --> 00:11:50.987 position:24% line:83% align:start
- Your dad said to
meet him at the tank.

00:11:51.020 --> 00:11:52.156 position:7% line:89% align:start
I'll show you how to get there.

00:11:52.189 --> 00:11:53.357 position:30% line:89% align:start
- [Ruka] Okay.

00:11:53.390 --> 00:11:54.191 position:35% line:89% align:start
Thank you.

00:12:10.541 --> 00:12:12.943 position:35% line:89% align:start
(laughing)

00:12:14.245 --> 00:12:15.346 position:33% line:89% align:start
- [Kid] Wow!

00:12:15.379 --> 00:12:17.381 position:38% line:89% align:start
(laughs)

00:12:20.251 --> 00:12:23.053 position:13% line:83% align:start
- If you head on in, you'll
be able to find him inside.

00:12:29.293 --> 00:12:30.160 position:41% line:89% align:start
Go on.

00:12:33.464 --> 00:12:35.399 position:21% line:83% align:start
Hey, be sure to check
out the Wonder Aquarium

00:12:35.432 --> 00:12:36.834 position:19% line:89% align:start
on your way out, okay?

00:12:36.867 --> 00:12:37.469 position:41% line:89% align:start
- Okay.

00:12:53.050 --> 00:12:54.219 position:41% line:89% align:start
Hello?

00:12:54.252 --> 00:12:55.119 position:44% line:89% align:start
Dad?

00:13:12.037 --> 00:13:12.904 position:44% line:89% align:start
Dad?

00:13:20.378 --> 00:13:21.579 position:24% line:89% align:start
Is anyone in here?

00:13:29.220 --> 00:13:30.589 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ow!

00:13:30.623 --> 00:13:32.957 position:35% line:89% align:start
(groaning)

00:13:52.378 --> 00:13:53.945 position:27% line:89% align:start
(water splashing)

00:13:53.978 --> 00:13:56.248 position:33% line:89% align:start
