01:38:52.759 --> 01:38:53.560 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ruka!

01:38:54.494 --> 01:38:55.730 position:21% line:89% align:start
- Ruka, hold onto me!

01:38:57.264 --> 01:38:58.131 position:44% line:89% align:start
Here.

01:39:02.703 --> 01:39:03.671 position:30% line:89% align:start
We've got you.

01:39:04.739 --> 01:39:06.339 position:41% line:89% align:start
- Ruka?

01:39:06.373 --> 01:39:07.173 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ruka?

01:39:11.344 --> 01:39:14.347 position:24% line:89% align:start
(seagull squawking)

01:39:45.680 --> 01:39:46.581 position:27% line:89% align:start
- [Man] Move it!

01:39:46.614 --> 01:39:47.548 position:21% line:89% align:start
- Come on, let's go!

01:39:47.582 --> 01:39:48.449 position:38% line:89% align:start
