01:39:54.255 --> 01:39:55.256 position:33% line:89% align:start
- Aw, great.

01:39:56.591 --> 01:39:58.492 position:24% line:89% align:start
Good bounty today.

01:39:58.526 --> 01:40:00.528 position:16% line:89% align:start
The seas were good to us.

01:40:25.387 --> 01:40:28.323 position:24% line:89% align:start
(string strumming)

01:40:51.413 --> 01:40:54.783 position:16% line:83% align:start
- I think I was probably
just about your age

01:40:56.318 --> 01:40:58.253 position:7% line:89% align:start
when I also met a beautiful boy

01:40:58.286 --> 01:40:59.488 position:19% line:89% align:start
who came from the sea.

01:41:01.490 --> 01:41:05.560 position:7% line:83% align:start
The children of the sea quietly
appear before us one day,

01:41:05.594 --> 01:41:07.529 position:30% line:83% align:start
and whisper the
stories of their truth.

01:41:11.601 --> 01:41:13.970 position:27% line:83% align:start
The stories about
where we came from

01:41:14.003 --> 01:41:15.505 position:19% line:89% align:start
and where we are going,

01:41:15.538 --> 01:41:17.473 position:16% line:89% align:start
and the reason we exist.

01:41:23.613 --> 01:41:26.749 position:13% line:83% align:start
