01:43:59.071 --> 01:44:01.806 position:30% line:89% align:start
(ball bouncing)

01:44:14.053 --> 01:44:15.788 position:19% line:89% align:start
- The sky and the sea.

01:44:19.825 --> 01:44:20.726 position:24% line:89% align:start
